(6, 'TR33', 'Scott Wyatt Rd.', 'White Water Paradise 33 Acres', '33.93 Acres - Huge chunk of East Tennessee acreage for sale by owner with many water features and great privacy.', '<h2>Description:</h2>\r\n<p>This is an awesome piece of East Tennessee land for sale by owner containing the remaining 33.93 acres in White Water Paradise. There are numerous homesites all over this land. It is perfect for a large estate tract, hunting land, recreation property, horse property, retirement or investment property. There are several existing ATV trails on this land as well as miles of trails on the Nature Preserve. There is a rocky branch on part of the property that has large sheer faced, rain fed waterfalls. The rocky branch would be great for hiking and exploring as the scenery on and around this land is amazing. A short hike from the property, through the nature preserve, brings you to the two miles of frontage on Clear Creek for almost endless kayaking. Partial ownership in the Nature Preserve comes with this purchase (a $12,500 value). The partial ownership gives you full access to 294 acres fronting 2 miles of the Clear Creek. This property would be ideal for kayaking, canoeing, rafting and camping. Hunting will be allowed on the preserve when population control is in effect. (Hunting on the 33.93 acres is not restricted.) Across the river is the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;cd=3&amp;ved=0CDEQFjAC&amp;url=http%253A%252F%252Fwww.tn.gov%252Ftwra%252Fgis%252Fwmapdf%252FCatoosa.pdf&amp;rct=j&amp;q=catoosa%20wildlife%20management%20area&amp;ei=hG1RTpvuJuiy0AHf4YTxBg&amp;usg=AFQjCNHLFgV9247KE1BViyGwlcJ_WheA2A&amp;sig2=gZ_4gwnimyhYgt5Y2w1umQ&amp;cad=rja">Catoosa Wildlife Management Area</a> giving you access to thousands of additional acres to play on!</p>\r\n<p>This land has over 600 ft of frontage on the gravel access road and 2398 ft of frontage bordering the nature preserve! A piece of East Tennessee land like this one doesn''t come around very often and when it''s gone... it''s gone!</p>\r\n<p>This land would also be perfect for white water enthusiasts as the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.riverfacts.com/rivers/13031.html">Clear Creek offers AW Class I-II rapids</a>.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Survey:</h2>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" title="White Water Paradise 33 Acre Land Survey" href="images/stories/tn_land/wwp/wwp_33ac/wwp%2033%20ac%20survey.jpg"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="images/stories/tn_land/wwp/wwp_33ac/wwp%2033%20ac%20survey.jpg" alt="Survey of 33 Acres of land at White Water Paradise for sale by owner" title="White Water Paradise 33 Acre Survey" width="575" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Geotagged Photos:</h2>\r\n<p>The below link contains photos from the 33 acre tract as well as the 294 acre nature preserve. You can see much of the 33 acre tract outline in the shape of the survey outlined by the blue tracts. The pictures going down to the Clear Creek are on the 294 acre Nature Preserve.</p>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" href="pages/east_tennessee_land_for_sale/whitewater_paradise/wwp_33ac/flash2/index.html"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="images/stories/tn_land/wwp/wwp_33ac/wwp_33ac_geotagged_photo_screenshot.jpg" title="Link to geotagged photos for 33 acre tract" width="575" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Land-Spin View of 33 Acre Tract:</h2>\r\n<p><iframe title="YouTube video player" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/8I3ybR5C4lM?rel=0&amp;hd=1" allowfullscreen="true" frameborder="0" height="353" width="575"></iframe></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>The "land-spin" concept was developed&nbsp;in order to better convey how the land we have for sale lies. We hope that the land spin view helps you get a better feel for this East Tennessee land for sale by owner!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Land-Spin View of 33 Acres, 294 Acre Nature Preserve and Adjacent Catoosa Wildlife Management Area:</h2>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://w