(49, 'TR127', 'Starlight Dr.', 'Meadowview 127.5 Acres', '127.5 Acres - Huge Northern Alabama mountain tract in Madison County right outside of Huntsville and Hampton Cove with awesome long range views.', '<h2>Description:</h2>\r\n<p>This is a recently surveyed 127.5 acres just outside of Huntsville, Alabama in Madison County. It is at the end of the road with power and public water in front of the property. This Northern Alabama acreage for sale by owner is just beyond the Hampton Cove community and the Robert Trent Jones Golf trail. Perfect location with the country, private feel yet close to all of today''s modern conveniences.</p>\r\n<p>This property has a roughed in drive leading up to an old, cleared off homesite. Homesite is level and has some really nice views. It has been perked already as well. The property is anywhere from level, to rolling, to mountainous. Lots of great rock formations and mostly all wooded. This would be a great hunting tract or a property for ATVs, camping, hiking or rock crawling. I saw signs of deer and turkey on the tract. There were also signs of possible springs on the land. A seasonal creek (Goose Creek) also runs through one corner of the tract.</p>\r\n<p>This land would be perfect for a private homestead or recreational property. Possibilities are endless. This land is priced to sell and won''t last long. Hard to find large acreage tracts in Madison County at an affordable price.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{modal url=/geotagging/tours/meadowview/meadowview_tour.html}Click here to take this land for a spin!{/modal} (You''ll need to have the <a target="_blank" href="http://earth.google.com/plugin/">Google Earth Plugin</a> installed and you may need to use the Firefox browser)</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Survey:</h2>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" href="images/stories/al_land/meadowview/meadowview%20survey.jpg"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="images/stories/al_land/meadowview/meadowview%20survey.j