(66, 'TR43', 'Beech Knob Rd.', 'Beech Knob 43 Acre Tract', '43.72 Acres - Large piece of owner financed land right outside of Huntsville Alabama with two small waterfalls and a cavern.', '<h2>Description:</h2>\r\n<p>43.72 Acres in Madison County.</p>\r\n<p>-30 minutes (16.6 mi) from the center of Huntsville. <br />-17 minutes (7.5 mi) from Hampton Cove Golf Course</p>\r\n<p>This owner financed land is perfect for the outdoorsman. There are signs of deer and turkey all over this tract. The terrain varies from level to rolling to mountainous and offers great views over Horse Cove and towards The Meadows at Hampton Cove. There are great rock formations to explore including a spring fed waterfall dropping around 30 feet into a good sized cavern.</p>\r\n<p>Here is a short video of the cavern:</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdFTs2iUXhI">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdFTs2iUXhI</a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>The tract has frontage on both Shooting Star Trail and Beech Knob Rd. There is an access road leading up on to the tract from Beech Knob Rd. The road has been neglected for a while and needs to have some work done. As it is now the road would make for a great rock crawling trail for Jeeps, Side by Sides or ATV''s. The property has numerous great homesites with views for miles.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Survey of Alabama Land for Sale:</h2>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" href="images/stories/al_land/beech_knob/43ac_tract/beechknobplat.jpg"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="images/stories/al_land/beech_knob/43ac_tract/beechknobplat.jpg" alt="Survey of Huntsville, Alabama Land for Sale - Beech Knob 43 Acre - Owner Financed Alabama Land" title="Beech Knob 43 Acre Land Survey" width="575" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Geotagged Photos:</h2>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" href="pages/alabama_land_for_sale/beech_knob/43_72_acres/flash/index.html"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="images/stories/al_land/beech_knob/43ac_tract/beech%20knob%2043%20acre%20geotagged%20screen%20shot.jpg" alt="Link to Geotagged Photos of Beech Knob Land" title="Link to Geotagged Photos of Beech Knob Land" width="575" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>Land-Spin View:</h2>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/MxiZHU_i48U?rel=0&amp;hd=1" allowfullscreen="true" frameborder="0" height="357" width="575"></iframe></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>The "land-spin" concept was developed&nbsp;in order to better convey how the land we have for sale lies. With this land, you can see how the land is on the side of a ridge with the possibility of great views into the valley. The land for sale touches the paved county road and would be an ideal spot to bring in utilities to a nice dream home up on the mountain. There is also a dirt road (Beech Knob Road) that borders much of the land''s perimeter. The road hasn''t been used in a while so it has washed out in spots but it wouldn''t take much to get it drivable again. This road would be the prefered way to access this land and get to the nice homesites up top. We hope that the land spin view helps you get a better feel for this AL land for sale by owner right outside of Huntsville.</p>', 'Gurley', 1, '35748', 'Madison', '34.653016', '-86.378594', '', '103500.00', 44, 336, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
