(175, 'TR1A', 'Campground RD', 'Powder House Hills Tract 1A', '5.18 acres of peaceful rural acreage for under $250 monthly', '<p><span>This 5.18 acres is located in a peaceful rural area of </span>Scott County(East Tennessee). &nbsp;This property lays very well with hills and level areas. &nbsp;The property is a mixture of hardwoods and pines. &nbsp;This property could make a great setting for a mini farm or use it as your recreational getaway for hunting or? &nbsp;Easy owner financing on this land and payments under $250. &nbsp;Additional 5 acres is available that could easily be turned into pasture.</p>', 'Sunbright', 43, '37872', 'Scott', '36.30468129357496', '-84.60378170013428', '', '28000.00', 5, 505, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(173, 'Powell River Tract 1', 'Powell River Rd', '31 acres on the Powell River', 'Great recreational land in East Tennessee with owner financing.  This property fronts the Powell River and also borders a state wildlife management area.', '<h2>This property is located in Harrogate TN near the KY state line. &nbsp;The property is very hilly and secluded. &nbsp;This 31.52 acres has 200'' of frontage on the Powell River. &nbsp;The Powell River is the second most biologically diverse river in America. &nbsp;This river offers great fishing and other recreational activities like kayaking and canoeing. &nbsp;There are many good sites on this property where you could build a home, cabin or park your RV. &nbsp;There is also a roughed in driveway that leads onto the property and gets you back into the hills more than a 1/4 mile from the road. &nbsp;This property has the remains of an old barn and a log shed from many years ago. &nbsp;This property also borders a Tennessee State Wildlife area. &nbsp;If you don''t need a tract this large...we also have an 11 acre tract on the Powell River. &nbsp;Call for details.</h2>', 'Harrogate', 43, '37752', 'Claiborne', '36.55556786121835', '-83.58973503112793', '', '89000.00', 32, 1552, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
